name: Lunicorns
description: All Lunicorns are frens, but some are cooler than others. That’s why we’ve established a trait rarity system to tell which are likely destined for greatness. There are 120+ total traits in the club and these have been categorized into a tier based system. Traits are ranked from ‘common’ all the way through to ‘legendary’ and each rank has a corresponding % chance of being minted.
